Package: casper
Type: Package
Title: Class and methods for hyperspectral data
Version: 0.0.1
Author: as.person("Jose Eduardo Meireles <meireles@umn.edu> [aut, cre]")
Maintainer: Jose Eduardo Meireles <meireles@umn.edu>
Description: Provides the S3 class `spectra` for hyperspectral data and methods
    to access and manipulate spectral data. The goal is to provide a common interface for
    spectra that other packages can build on.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL3
